HEADWORD: Feudalism
<hw>Feu"dal*ism</hw> <pr>(f⟦umac⟧"d⟦ait⟧l*⟦icr⟧z'm)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Cf. F. <ets>f⟦eacute⟧odalisme</ets>.]</ety> <def>The feudal
